name: American Vintage Textured Zip-Up Hoodie
description: A full zip-up hoodie from American Vintage in a soft ecru color. Crafted from 100% cotton, this sweatshirt features a distinct, cozy texture resembling terry cloth or a slub knit. It is designed with a comfortable, relaxed fit with dropped shoulders for an effortless look. Functional details include an adjustable drawstring hood, a full-length front zipper, and two front pouch pockets. The cuffs and hem are finished with classic ribbed trim.

name: Nike Sportswear Essential Zip Hoodie
description: A women's full-zip hoodie from Nike Sportswear in a soft, muted salmon color. Made from a comfortable cotton and polyester blend jersey fabric, this hoodie is ideal for everyday wear and layering. It features a clean, minimalist design with a standard fit, a simple non-adjustable hood, and a full-length front zipper. For storage, it includes two discreet front welt pockets. The look is completed with a classic white Nike swoosh embroidered on the left chest.

name: Puma Tie-Dye Graphic Hoodie
description: A women's pullover hoodie from Puma, featuring a striking all-over tie-dye pattern in shades of red and burnt orange. Made from soft 100% cotton, this sweatshirt offers a comfortable and relaxed fit ideal for casual wear. It includes classic hoodie features such as an adjustable drawstring hood with off-white cords, a large front kangaroo pocket, and ribbed cuffs and hem. A square graphic with the Puma wordmark and a stylized floral symbol is printed on the chest in a contrasting off-white color.

name: American Vintage Oversized Logo Hoodie
description: An oversized zip-up hoodie from American Vintage, presented in a solid black color. Crafted from a heavyweight, comfortable cotton blend with a touch of elastane for added stretch, this piece is designed for a modern, relaxed silhouette with prominent dropped shoulders. It features a full-length front zipper, a large adjustable hood with thick, contrasting off-white drawstrings, and two front pouch pockets. A minimalist 'American Vintage' logo is printed in white on the left chest.

name: Champion Garment-Dyed Cropped Hoodie
description: A women's cropped zip-up hoodie from Champion, featuring a vintage aesthetic achieved through a garment-dyed finish in a muted teal blue. Crafted from a heavyweight and soft cotton-polyester blend fleece, this hoodie offers premium comfort and durability. The design features a modern, boxy and cropped silhouette with dropped shoulders for a relaxed feel. It includes a full-length metal zipper, a spacious hood, two front pouch pockets, and wide ribbed detailing on the cuffs and hem. The iconic Champion 'C' logo is subtly embroidered on the left sleeve cuff.

name: American Vintage Textured Zip-Up Hoodie
description: A full zip-up hoodie from American Vintage in a charcoal grey color, distinguished by its highly textured, plush fabric. Crafted from 100% cotton, the material has a cozy, terry cloth or bouclé-like feel. This sweatshirt is designed for a relaxed fit and features dropped shoulders with exposed seam detailing for a modern touch. It includes a full-length front zipper, an adjustable hood with thick, contrasting cream-colored drawstrings, and two front pouch pockets. The cuffs and hem are finished with comfortable ribbed trim.

name: American Vintage Boxy Logo Sweatshirt
description: A women's crewneck sweatshirt from American Vintage, presented in a washed, sage green color for a lived-in, vintage feel. Crafted from a heavyweight and soft cotton blend with a hint of elastane for comfortable stretch, this piece is designed with a modern, boxy and slightly cropped silhouette. It features relaxed, dropped shoulders and is finished with a ribbed crew neck, cuffs, and hem. A tonal 'AMERICAN VINTAGE' logo is printed on the left chest for a subtle, minimalist branding touch.

name: Dickies Acid Wash Logo Sweatshirt
description: A men's crewneck sweatshirt from Dickies featuring a distinct vintage look, achieved through an acid wash or garment-dye process in a faded slate blue. Crafted from a durable and comfortable cotton-polyester blend fleece, this sweatshirt is designed for a relaxed fit. It features classic ribbed detailing on the crew neck, cuffs, and hem. A tonal 'Dickies' script logo is embroidered on the left chest for a subtle branding effect, complemented by the signature Dickies woven tab stitched at the hem.

name: !SOLID 'El Buen Vivir' Embroidered Sweatshirt
description: A men's long-sleeve crewneck sweatshirt from !SOLID in a solid olive green, perfect as a lightweight layer. Crafted from soft 100% cotton jersey, this piece features a classic standard fit with a ribbed collar and cuffs for everyday comfort. The left chest is adorned with a detailed and colorful embroidery inspired by leisure, depicting an open book, a wine bottle, and a glass. The graphic is captioned with the Spanish phrase 'El Buen Vivir' (The Good Living). The back remains unembellished for a clean, versatile look.

name: Kaotiko 'I Love Drama' Hoodie
description: A men's oversized pullover hoodie from the streetwear brand Kaotiko, featured in a faded, garment-washed sage green. Crafted from heavyweight 100% cotton fleece, this hoodie provides a premium feel with a structured, boxy silhouette. It is designed with a very relaxed fit, dropped shoulders, a large front kangaroo pocket, and a simple hood without drawstrings. The chest features a large, ironic graphic print of two swans forming a heart, framed by the phrase 'I LOVE DRAMA', with 'KAOTIKO SOCIETY' printed below.

name: Champion Script Logo Crewneck Sweatshirt
description: A classic men's crewneck sweatshirt from Champion in solid black, embodying timeless athletic style. Crafted from a comfortable and durable cotton-polyester blend fleece, this sweatshirt offers both warmth and softness for everyday wear. It is designed for a relaxed fit and features a ribbed crew neck, cuffs, and hem. The chest is adorned with the iconic Champion script logo in a large, screen-printed graphic. The signature embroidered 'C' logo patch is stitched onto the left sleeve cuff, adding an authentic touch.

name: Sprayground Shark Mouth Bandana Hoodie
description: A men's pullover hoodie from the streetwear brand Sprayground in solid black, featuring unique, integrated accessories. Crafted from premium 100% cotton heavyweight fleece, this hoodie has a comfortable and structured relaxed fit. Its standout feature is a custom-printed bandana with the brand's shark mouth graphic, built directly into the hood. The iconic shark mouth is also embroidered on the side of the hood, peeking out. The design is completed with a classic kangaroo pocket, ribbed cuffs and hem, and 'SPRAYGROUND' branding printed on the sleeve cuffs.

name: adidas x 100 Thieves Collaboration Hoodie
description: A limited edition pullover hoodie from the collaboration between adidas Originals and lifestyle/esports brand 100 Thieves. Featured in a dark charcoal grey, this hoodie is covered in an all-over tonal embroidered pattern resembling a topographical map or abstract camouflage, giving it a unique, textured look. The design includes the iconic adidas three stripes in black along the sleeves. The chest features the collaboration's co-branding, with the adidas Trefoil logo above the '100 Thieves' wordmark. Crafted from premium fleece fabric for comfort, it has a classic pullover construction with a spacious hood and ribbed cuffs and hem.

name: adidas x Wales Bonner Track Hoodie
description: A premium full zip-up hoodie from the celebrated collaboration between adidas Originals and designer Grace Wales Bonner. Inspired by archival 70s tracksuits, this hoodie is crafted from a smooth tricot fabric with a signature retro sheen in a rich burgundy color. Designed for a relaxed fit, it features a full-length zipper, an adjustable hood with thick, contrasting braided drawstrings, and two front welt pockets. The left chest is adorned with a co-branded circular embroidered patch, featuring the adidas Trefoil and 'WB CLUB' insignia, paying homage to vintage sports clubs.

name: Dickies Sherpa Fleece Half-Zip Pullover
description: A men's relaxed fit pullover from Dickies, crafted from high-pile sherpa fleece in a solid khaki color. Made from 100% polyester, this fleece offers exceptional warmth and a soft, textured feel, making it ideal for colder weather. The design features a stand-up collar (mock neck) with a half-zip closure for adjustable ventilation. It includes a large kangaroo-style front pocket for hand warming and storage. The signature Dickies woven logo tab is stitched onto the chest for a touch of authentic branding.
